{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, previous studies [43,54] suggest that incorporating the chart-to-table translation task improves VL models' general chart understanding performance, while its effect within the context of MLLMs merits deeper investigation.",
    "Computational Analysis of ChartQA DatasetTo address RQ1, we conduct computational analyses of ChartQA's distribution in terms of chart and QA pairs.",
    "We identify distribution bias by comparing them with practical charts and visual literacy data.",
    "Subsequently, we assess the performance of various MLLMs on ChartQA and contrast these results with performances in real-world scenarios, emphasizing the impacts of distribution bias on model performance.",
    "Distribution Biases in Chart and QA PairsChart distribution."
  ]
}